        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1447",
        "content": "Either fortunately or unfortunately-I cannot say-you have no need of such a book in America.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
