        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1447",
        "content": "He is neither a count nor of noble family, although I suppose when you met him in New York he had an object in posing as a titled aristocrat.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
