        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1447",
        "content": "It will be better to avoid him.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1447_17506_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1447/17506/1447_17506_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1447",
        "content": "\"He-he seems very nice and gentlemanly,\" said Louise with hesitation.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1447_17506_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1447/17506/1447_17506_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1447",
        "content": "The other girls exchanged glances, but made no remark.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
